sourcesContent: import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { UnityService } from '../unity.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-home', templateUrl: './home.component.html', styleUrls: ['./home.component.css'] }) export class HomeComponent { speed:number = 2; objectsAmount:number = 30; timeInSeconds:number = 0; constructor(private unityService:UnityService){ this.testConnection() } async testConnection(){ (await this.unityService.testConnection()).subscribe(value => console.log(value.message)); } }
